Clair Obscur Expedition 33 Verso Guide -  How to Play Verso (Build Tips)
In this Clair obscur Expedition 33 guide, we break down  Verso’s best skills, weapons, and strategies to maximize his effectiveness in battle. Whether you're looking for solo builds, counter-based strategies, or team synergies, this guide will help you optimize Verso for boss fights, exploration, and late-game encounters.
